nl.fw.yapool.sql.datasource

Class DataSourceProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.fw.yapool.sql.datasource.MockByProxy
      • nl.fw.yapool.sql.datasource.DataSourceProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InvocationHandler

    public class DataSourceProxy
extends MockByProxy
    A proxy for DataSource backed by a SqlProxyPool.
    Proxy is used to prevent compile errors (DataSource changed between Java 1.6 and Java 1.7).
    Connections requested from this DataSource are taken from the pool and are also proxied (see ConnectionProxy) so that connections are returned to the pool instead of closed.
    Author:
    FWiers
